This file is a record of changes between released versions.

Version 1.6 - simple fixes and clean up
	: include Makefile.simple in post.
	: support for black and white (see xw.c)
	: an ASCII high score file - more portable and 'tote-able'
	: clean up and changed all references from 'jewel' to 'xjewel'

Version 1.5 - first released to alt.sources
	: clean up and support for VMS including help.

Version 1.4 and earlier - beta
